description: Located in the West Side of South Boston, 288 Athens Street is situated in one of Boston’s fastest growing and most diverse submarkets. This three unit multifamily property consists of two (2) two bedroom style units and one (1) three bedroom unit across +/- 3,000 square feet. Each unit comes equipped with a fully renovated kitchen and bathroom featuring stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, an in-unit washer and dryer, and a private deck as an added feature.
